## Epilogue_Seth_Duessel
Seth, for his part, continued to serve Renais[N]
with distinction, not only as a general but as[N]
a mentor to the kingdom's future leaders.[N]
Inspired by the advice of Duessel, Seth helped[N]
guide Renais into an era of peace, where the bonds[N]
of trust and hope became as strong as the armor of[N]
its knights. Though the two generals served[N]
different kingdoms, they remained close friends[N]
and often exchanged letters, sharing the lessons[N]
they continued to learn in peace as they had once[N]
done in war.[A][X]
